name: Trapped in Phone
description:
This is a model that's based on the concept of phone screensavers where the character is trapped in the phone. I've seen this concept work anywhere between 0.6 and 1 so play with it to suit your needs. This model was trained on NAI anime-full-pruned and generated in AOM3. Made with the Kohya tool for AI Training. Any suggestions to improve or recommended things for the data set would be appreciated.
I highly recommend using the
bad hands embedding
Since any front facing waifu will have there hands on the screen normally.

modelVersions.name: Trapped in Phone V1
modelVersions.description: Hand on glass being the most common tends to happen even if unprompted. Cleaning screen makes the glass wet but not much else you may want to also prompt cleaning supplies for full effect. If doing an ass on glass I suggest hiding the hands since the palms will probably be backwards (something to work on later on). If it starts doing backgrounds put 'black background' in positives and 'bathroom' in negatives. Suggestions to improve are appreciated or even just more good images for the dataset. Very fun little lora.
